description: Torslanda Property Investment AB engages in the indirect ownership, management and lease of real estate. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2015-01-29. The company owns, manages and rents the property Sorred 8:4 in Gothenburg, an office building leased by Volvo PV. The firm is managed by a property manager, Wilfast Forvaltning AB. Its property comprises approximately 49,000 square meters of office space occupied by Volvo PV Forskning och Utveckling, as well as two garages with around 2,900 parking places. The firm has one subsidiary, Gothenburg PVH AB.
name: Torslanda Property Investment AB (publ)
